#Text=Well yeah .
#Text=All I was presented with was life as it was deconstructing and disintegrating .
#Text=And I had to pick up whatever pieces I had off the floor and try to put it together in a way that made sense to me .
#Text=I do n’t know if I ’m making myself all that clear .
#Text=I really love what I do and I do n’t want people to think I ’m sitting here angry all the time .
#Text=I ’m absolutely happy and I like what my life has become .
#Text=But I still will start feeling weird if somebody asks me a question and I ca n’t tell the truth about it .
#Text=I ’m just telling it like it is .
#Text=— Billy West
#Text=No you are .
#Text=Yeah , I ’m telling you stuff that I never said to anybody .
#Text=Well it ’s good .
#Text=You ’re like the Barbara Walters of your generation .
#Text=And I ’m not going to protect an image I do n’t really have .
#Text=Nobody wants to hear what I really think about politics .
#Text=I totally understand it .
#Text=It ’s like , every night is opening night if you ’re a performer .
#Text=Okay that ’s done .
#Text=Now what ?
#Text=I mean if everyone had to answer that standard in their job .
#Text=" Now what are you going to do ? "
#Text=Because I do n’t get told what to do .
#Text=I audition for everything because if you want to work you ’ve got to audition .
#Text=Some people call me out of the blue and say , ' We just want you , ' which is very nice and I worked really hard for that status .
#Text=But I still audition for everything .
#Text=There ’s a show coming up called Rahan and there ’s a 26 episode commitment on that .
#Text=I ’ll be starting that soon .
#Text=I ca n’t tell you much about it because I ’ve only read the auditions , the lines I was supposed to do .
#Text=And the other thing is Futurama is going to keep me busy for awhile even though all the voice-over work is done .
#Text=There ’s lots of projects that are related to it .
#Text=And I ’m still doing the M&Ms .
#Text=I really love what I do and I do n’t want people to think I ’m sitting here angry all the time .
#Text=I ’m absolutely happy and I like what my life has become .
#Text=But I still will start feeling weird if somebody asks me a question and I ca n’t tell the truth about it .
#Text=I ’m just telling it like it is .
#Text=That 's perfect .
#Text=I will send you a link to the interview when it is published .
#Text=That would be fine .
#Text=I ’d appreciate it .
#Text=There 's so much wrong on Wikipedia , like that I got booted off the Stern show .
#Text=I feel a lot of dehumanized lie dispensers get a hold of these things and just make it so .
#Text=Believe me , there ’s this very small but very active group of posters that want to keep dancing in the pet cemetery with animal corpses .
